# Redirect All CTA Buttons to WhatsApp, Update Contact Details, Fix Featured Resources

## Summary

Replace all form-based booking/consultation flows with direct WhatsApp links, update the Clarity Session button to link to a Selar clarity call page, update contact details across the site, add a `featured` field to resources, and keep form-gating only for resource downloads.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Selar Clarity Call Link**: You mentioned "Clarity session should direct to the clarity call link — the seller link." I need the **exact Selar URL** for the clarity call (e.g., `https://selar.co/your-product-id`). Please provide this link so I can wire it up correctly.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **WhatsApp Phone Number**: The current WhatsApp sticky uses a placeholder number `2348123456789`. The contact number you gave is `08135134528` which translates to `2348135134528` in international format. Should I use **2348135134528** for all WhatsApp links?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **WhatsApp Default Messages**: Currently there's one default message. Should different buttons have different pre-filled messages? For example:
> - "Book Demo" → `Hi, I'd like to book a growth consultation.`
> - "Book Strategy Session" → `Hi, I'd like to book a strategy session.`
> - "Speak With Our Team" → `Hi, I'd like to speak with your team.`
> - Or should all buttons use the same generic message?

---

## Open Questions

