## Proposed Changes

### 1. Create a Centralized WhatsApp Config

#### [NEW] [whatsapp.ts](file:///home/frank/Documents/digitalife/src/lib/whatsapp.ts)

Create a single source of truth for WhatsApp URL generation and contact details so all components reference the same phone number and we can easily change it later.

```ts
export const WHATSAPP_PHONE = '2348135134528';
export const CONTACT_EMAIL = 'Digitaligehub@gmail.com';
export const CONTACT_ADDRESS = 'Okpu umuobo, Aba, Abia state, Nigeria';
export const CONTACT_PHONE = '08135134528';
export const SELAR_CLARITY_CALL_URL = 'https://selar.co/PLACEHOLDER'; // User to provide

export function getWhatsAppUrl(message?: string): string {
  const defaultMsg = 'Hi Digitalife Ehub, I am interested in scaling and structuring my business.';
  const text = encodeURIComponent(message || defaultMsg);
  return `https://wa.me/${WHATSAPP_PHONE}?text=${text}`;
}
```

