## Change Summary Table

| Location | Current Behavior | New Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| All "Book" / "Consult" / "Get Started" buttons | Opens `BookingModal` (form) | Opens WhatsApp chat link in new tab |
| "Clarity Call" buttons | Opens `BookingModal` | Links to Selar clarity call URL |
| Footer email | `info@digitalifeehub.com` | `Digitaligehub@gmail.com` |
| Footer address | `Lagos, Nigeria` | `Okpu umuobo, Aba, Abia state, Nigeria` |
| Footer phone | Not shown | `08135134528` |
| Privacy email | `info@digitalifeehub.com` | `Digitaligehub@gmail.com` |
| WhatsApp sticky phone | `2348123456789` (placeholder) | `2348135134528` (real) |
| Featured Resources section | Shows all resources in category | Shows only `featured: true` resources |
| Resource download forms | Email gate / checkout | **No change** (stays as form) |
| `BookingModal` component | Renders modal with form | **Removed entirely** |

